dc_description_s: 1 map : hand col. ; 45 x 55 cm|Relief shown pictorially.|Top border has views of Cuzco, Mexico City, Olinda, Havanna, Santo Domingo and Cartagena.|Left and right borders have images of indigenous peoples.|Decorative cartouche with a native person riding an armadillo.|Lower left has image of Neptune and his queen riding sea horses.
